{"tid":1830442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《有圖》吳鎮宇屌醒你地班香港人","createTime":"2020-01-19T15:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T12:01:35.000Z","uid":220066,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"163d5255bdd7046c08b3b8a752fd6275a7ad3572","tid":1830442,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"吳鎮宇曾經講過法律係由當權者負責訂立<br />\n既然我地嘅權益比政府剝削<br />\n咁點解我地仲要咁on9堅守政府所訂立既規則<br />\n<br />\n吳鎮宇講過：<br />\n「世界對你唔公平，就要企出嚟抗爭」<br />\n「唔滿意呢個建制，就走入建制裏面拆散佢」<br />\n<br />\n點解仲有咁多香港人仲要比當權者帶住遊花園<br />\n仲相信香港司法制度仲能夠可以把關<br />\n唔好咁天真啦好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adRy6Ro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadRy6Ro.png&h=9216e32c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QVj2pK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QVj2pK.png&h=5a2506d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjgSCX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjgSCX8.png&h=a1599a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mo2fKP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mo2fKP.png&h=cd30126b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hiCFMRw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiCFMRw.png&h=f6b436aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d82c6e5ff718770da8ba7839a2cb749ac0f7d66","tid":1830442,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"討論：香港人可唔可以全球登報 發起全球大罷工 向外國政府施壓制裁中共？<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1830351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1830351</a>"},{"pid":"07b167ca3e6156dff32000ee2b1f9f326bcaf34c","tid":1830442,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"318475737c76ed3578c4578d83aab939b8096708","tid":1830442,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:07:20.000Z"